Package common

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAddReceiverType
    Common data type for adding receiver.
    IChatRoom
    A generalized chat room interface that defines a set of operations of a chat room.
    ICmd2ModelAdapter
    This adapter is for the externally-sourced commands to interact with the local model
    IComponentFactory
    A factory for creating desired GUI components.
    IExceptionStatusType
    IExceptionStatusType is a sub interface of IFailureStatusType, defines a concrete failure status due to exception
    IFailureStatusType
    Common data type for failure status.
    IInstallCmdType
    Common data type for transmitting command between remote peers.
    IReceiver
    IReceiver defines a receiver in a chat room, which corresponds to a user (More accurately, a remote user's chat room) in the remote.
    IRejectionStatusType
    IRejectionStatusType is a sub interface of IFailureStatusType, defines a concrete failure status due to rejection.
    IRemoveReceiverType
    Common data type for removing receiver.
    IRequestCmdType
    Common data type for sending a message that a specific command is needed for processing a certain type of data packet.
    IUser
    IUser interface defines a set of operations of a user in our chatApp IUser is NOT transmitted to anyone.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataPacketAlgoCmd<T>
    Specialized data packet processing command that uses DataPacketChatRoom<T> and ICmd2ModelAdapters.
    DataPacketChatRoom<T>
    A more concrete data packet that holds a generic type of data.
